  "body": "Seen in https://github.com/coder/coder/actions/runs/4364182125/jobs/7631187781#step:9:184\r\n\r\nIt looks like we try to query providers on each unit test. This is a sure-fire recipe for flakes.\r\n\r\n```\r\n=== Failed\r\n=== FAIL: provisioner/terraform TestProvision/single-resource-dry-run (0.42s)\r\n    t.go:81: 2023-03-08 12:16:53.984 [DEBUG]\t<github.com/coder/coder/provisioner/terraform/provision.go:124>\t(*server).Provision\trunning initialization\r\n    provision_test.go:422: log: [DEBUG] \r\n    provision_test.go:422: log: [DEBUG] Initializing the backend...\r\n    provision_test.go:422: log: [DEBUG] \r\n    provision_test.go:422: log: [DEBUG] Initializing provider plugins...\r\n    provision_test.go:422: log: [DEBUG] - Finding latest version of hashicorp/null...\r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] \r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] Error: Failed to query available provider packages\r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] \r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] Could not retrieve the list of available versions for provider\r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] hashicorp/null: could not connect to registry.terraform.io: Failed to request\r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] discovery document: Get\r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] \"https://registry.terraform.io/.well-known/terraform.json\": read tcp\r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] 10.79.0.105:5[198](https://github.com/coder/coder/actions/runs/4364182125/jobs/7631187781#step:9:199)7->18.165.116.100:443: read: connection reset by peer\r\nError: vision_test.go:422: log: [ERROR] \r\n    provision_test.go:429: \r\n        \tError Trace:\t/Users/runner/work/coder/coder/provisioner/terraform/provision_test.go:429\r\n        \t            \t\t\t\t/Users/runner/work/coder/coder/provisioner/terraform/provision_test.go:469\r\n        \tError:      \tReceived unexpected error:\r\n        \t            \tinitialize terraform: exit status 1\r\n        \t            \t\tstorj.io/drpc/drpcwire.UnmarshalError:26\r\n        \t            \t\tstorj.io/drpc/drpcstream.(*Stream).HandlePacket:198\r\n        \t            \t\tstorj.io/drpc/drpcmanager.(*Manager).manageReader:216\r\n        \tTest:       \tTestProvision/single-resource-dry-run\r\n\r\n=== FAIL: provisioner/terraform TestProvision (0.00s)\r\n```",
